cconf is a  small and smart build assistant.
cconf aims to be a very lightweight and easy to use build assistant
(like auto*, but with fun).

## how to get it?

### git

 * git-clone http://unix.schottelius.org/git/cLinux/cconf
 * [gitweb](http://git.schottelius.org/?p=cLinux/cconf;a=summary)

